title: Snake Island
description:
In this Ben Cropp production we are taken to Niue; the beautiful, uplifted atoll situated in the Central Pacific, 4000km north of Australia. Honeycombed with limestone caves, Niue is a speck of land in a vast ocean of sea snakes and humpback whales.

We join Cropp as he explores both the islands colourful wildlife, and the people that inhibit it. The island lies in the migratory path of the great Humpback whale, and it is here they come to calve and mate. We are taken on many dives in which the team capture wonderful underwater footage of these gentle giants.

Join the team as they go in search of Snake Gully, the location where sea snakes, indigenous only to the island, come ashore to lay their eggs. It is estimated that around 90% of the hatchlings will be eaten in there first year. Their first test is to make it past the sharks that circle
the island.

Cropp and his team then take us to another part of the island to meet some of the locals to find out more about their culture and their way of life. We find a new church has just been opened, and everyone joins in the celebrations. It is the Niue way to give money and gifts to all the performers at such an event, who perform a dance for all visitors of the island. 

Among the splendid array of scenery and wildlife captured during the filming the team make one last extraordinary discovery when they return to their diving spot to find a baby whale has been born.

title: Honey bee decline spreading globally
description:
Saturday, March 12, 2011

Scientists working for the United Nations Environment Programme (UNEP) reported Thursday that the collapse of honey bee colonies is becoming a world wide phenomenon and will continue unless humans work to restore habitats for bees. The insects are necessary for pollinating crops and the report calls for profound changes in how humans manage the planet.
The decline in managed bee colonies, first noticed in Europe and the U.S., is now seen in China and Japan, and there are signs of colony collapses in Egypt. According to the U.S. Department of Agriculture, honey-producing colonies in the U.S. have declined from 5.5 million colonies in 1950 to 2.5 million in 2007. A co-author of the report, Peter Neumann, said changes in rural areas during the past 50 years have contributed to decline of wild bees and other pollinators. Additional factors include the declines in flowering plants, the use of harmful chemicals and insecticides, the increase in air pollution and a worldwide trade system that spreads bee pathogens and pests.
The world's growing population means more bees are needed to pollinate the crops to feed more people. According to the U.N. report, of the 100 crop species that supply 90 percent of the world's food, bees pollinate more than 70 percent. Noting that humans seem to believe that they can operate independent of nature through technological innovations, Achim Steiner, the executive director of the UNEP said, "Bees underline the reality that we are more, not less dependent on nature's services in a world of close to 7 billion people."
The report calls for such measures as incentives for farmers and land owners to encourage them to restore habitats that are friendly to pollinators.

title: PPTour 2010 - 4ª tappa: Nova Gorica - Il Backstage
description: Neanche il tempo di dire amen, e la coppia più insonne della famiglia People's ha sfornato un altro piccolo capolavoro: il backstage della tappa di Nova Gorica.  Gli autori, già tante volte apprezzati, sono il mago delle telecamere Fabio Costantino e il re del mixer Gilberto Mauriello. Il Backstage è una sequenza delle scene più divertenti distillate da ore di registrazione. La preparazione e il dietro le quinte della tappa più spettacolare del PPT trasmette, contemporaneamente, la gioia e la fatica di chi allestisce e governa una macchina sempre più complessa. Alcune acrobazie aeree per fissare telecamere e lampadine meriterebbero da sole, come si suol dire, il viaggio...

title: 1955 CHRYSLER NEW YORKER DELUXE NEWPORT - ONE OF 5,777
description: Three Chrysler models were offered this year:  The Windsor Deluxe, the New Yorker Deluxe and the famous hemi-powered 300.  The Chrysler Imperial was a seperate make under the Chrysler Corp. umbrella.  Both the Windsor and New Yorker models offered a four door sedan, hardtop coupe, convertible coupe, and Town and Country wagons.  The Windsor model was powered by a V8 301 cid / 188 bhp., and the New Yorker had a V8 331 cid / 250 bhp.  ( The 300 also used the 331 cid but with 300 horses) .  This 2-door New Yorker hardtop would have put you back around $3,652 bucks, a princely sum in 1955.  This Saphire White over Canyon Tan example is outstanding in it's condition.  The interior is in original condition and well preserved.  I noticed that the steering wheel hub states " power steering ".   Notice also the twin tower taillamps and the front to back trim.  This New Yorker is a prime example of the Chrysler products " Forward Look" design and you can see the quality of this vehicle all around.  Thanks very much for viewing this long titled 1955 Chrysler New Yorker Deluxe Newport.

title: Damascus Friction Folder
description:
Alabama Damascus Steel - Alabama Buckshot Pattern Billet
Material = (4) layers 5160, (3) layers 203E, (3) layers 52100, (3) layers 15N20 folded 5 times for 416 layer damascus.
Damascus steel was a type of steel used in South Asian and Middle Eastern swordmaking. Damascus steel was created from wootz steel, a steel developed in India around 300 BC. These swords are characterized by distinctive patterns of banding and mottling reminiscent of flowing water. Such blades were reputed to be tough, resistant to shattering and capable of being honed to a sharp, resilient edge.
The original method of producing Damascus steel is not known. Because of differences in raw materials and manufacturing techniques, modern attempts to duplicate the metal have not been entirely successful. Despite this, several individuals in modern times have claimed that they have rediscovered the methods in which the original Damascus steel was produced.
The reputation and history of Damascus steel has given rise to many legends, such as the ability to cut through a rifle barrel or to cut a hair falling across the blade, but no evidence exists to support such claims. A research team in Germany published a report in 2006 revealing nanowires and carbon nanotubes in a blade forged from Damascus steel This finding was covered by National Geographic and the New York Times. Although modern steel outperforms these swords, microscopic chemical reactions in the production process may have made the blades extraordinary for their time. Woody biomass and leaves are known to have been used to carbonize the Wootz ingots used in Damascus steel, and research now shows that carbon nanotubes can be derived from plant fibers, suggesting how the nanotubes were formed in the steel. Some experts expect to discover such nanotubes in more relics as they are analyzed more closely.

Justice-WoW - Instant 86. PvP Realm & a PvE Leveling / Raiding Realm (completely Fun Server WIth high Rates), Version 2.4.3.

- What's the server like?

Justice WoW is unique, and different compared to other 2.4.3 PvP servers.

 

You'll start out at level 70, with a mall to obtain Deluxe Tier6 Gear for free, as well as Rings, Trinkets, Necks, and the other pieces.(On the Npc vendor By Cliking on your class as i said).

 

You'll be able to work for Aerolite And Ultimate Gear by doing Quest,Bosses, and getting Tokens, and you'll also be able to obtain Awesome Weapons by doing some PvP.

description:
Official music video for the brand new single, "Sink" which will be featured on a 4-way split with They All Float, Distances, and Corkscrew. The split will be pressed on a limited number of vinyl records and released through Nothing Special Records in late spring 2014.

Pre-order vinyl (not final art): http://nothingspecialrecs.storenvy.com/products/5440693-7-split-corkscrew-day-in-day-out-distances-they-all-float

Pre-order digital: http://nothingspecialrecords.bandcamp.com/

Download Sink: https://dayindayout.bandcamp.com/

Recorded/Mixed/Mastered by: Adam Cichocki at Timber Studios

We worked very hard to make a completely DIY video, and we weren't sure how it would turn out. The final product exceeds our expectations and proves that you don't have to go with a well-known company to make a high quality music video. Share this around and help get the word out about us, as well as the split that is coming out soon.

tags: ['The Last Stand trailer', 'The Last Stand movie', 'The Last Stand HD', 'HD', '2012', 'Kim Jee-Woon', 'Arnold Schwarzenegger', 'Forest Whitaker', 'Eduardo Noriega', 'Rodrigo Santoro', 'Johnny Knoxville', 'Jaimie Alexander', 'Peter Stormare', 'Zach Gilford', 'Genesis Rodriguez', 'action', 'luis guzman', 'daniel henney', 'movie', 'trailer', 'explosions', 'guns', 'thriller', 'comedy', 'corvette', 'cars', 'car chase']
description:
On January 18th... Arnold is BACK!

The Last Stand -- Official Final Trailer

Action icon Arnold Schwarzenegger makes his much-anticipated return to the big screen in Korean director Kim Jee-woon's hard-hitting US directorial debut, THE LAST STAND.

After leaving his LAPD narcotics post following a bungled operation that left him wracked with remorse and regret, Sheriff Ray Owens (Schwarzenegger) moved out of Los Angeles and settled into a life fighting what little crime takes place in sleepy border town Sommerton Junction. But that peaceful existence is shattered when Gabriel Cortez (Eduardo Noriega), the most notorious, wanted drug kingpin in the western hemisphere, makes a deadly yet spectacular escape from an FBI prisoner convoy.

With the help of a fierce band of lawless mercenaries led by the icy Burrell (Peter Stormare), Cortez begins racing towards the US-Mexico border at 250 mph in a specially-outfitted Corvette ZR1 with a hostage in tow. Cortez' path: straight through Summerton Junction, where the whole of the U.S. law enforcement, including Agent John Bannister (Forest Whitaker) will have their final opportunity to intercept him before the violent fugitive slips across the border forever.
At first reluctant to become involved, and then counted out because of the perceived ineptitude of his small town force, Owens ultimately rallies his team and takes the matter into his own hands, setting the stage for a classic showdown.
Arnold Schwarzenegger stars in THE LAST STAND. Directed by Kim Jee-woon and written by Andrew Knauer and Jeffrey Nachmanoff, THE LAST STAND also stars Forest Whitaker, Eduardo Noriega, Rodrigo Santoro, Johnny Knoxville, Jaimie Alexander, Luis Guzmán, Peter Stormare, Zach Gilford and Genesis Rodriguez. The film is produced by Lorenzo di Bonaventura (the TRANSFORMERS series, RED, GI JOE, SALT)."

title: Mercury Milan, Lincoln MKX with MyLincoln, & Lincoln MKZ Hybrid  at NYIAS 2010 - 4/9/2010
description: Here is the 2011 Lincoln MKX with the exterior features, and most of the features are also shared with the Ford Edge Crossover. MyLincoln and MyFord are part of the Microsoft Sync pacakage with intuitive controls with the climate, audio, navigation, and LED Screen of the instrument panel. The Lincoln MKZ Hybrid shares most of the features from the Ford Fusion and Mercury Milan Hybrids. Just like the Ford Fusion and Mercury Milan Hybrids, the exterior styling of the MKZ Hybrid is the same as the 2011 MKZ just to sort of forget that it's a Hybrid. But with the Hybrid badge, it is easy to tell that it's a Hybrid. It also gets the same fuel economy as the Fusion and Milan Hybrids, which actually beats the HS250h from Lexus and has 191 Horsepower with 2.4L Atkinsons Cycle engine with electric motor.

title: Dark Link Destroyed (First 4 Figures)
tags: ['Nintendo', 'Dark Link', 'Dark Link Exclusive', 'First 4 Figures', 'Collectables', 'Destroyed', 'The Legend of Zelda']
description:
A few months ago I received my Dark Link Exclusive Figure from First 4 Figures.  Sadly when it arrived I noticed that it's head fell off in the box.  This destroyed the wires that connect to the head allowing the eyes to glow.

I contacted First 4 Figures about the problem as was told another would be made and sent my way.  Now that the new figure is made for me, I had to destroy the original damaged product so that this awesome collectable stays as rare as it was originally meant to be.

First 4 Figures is awesome because they really care about their customers.  I really appreciate their dedication to making sure their fans get working versions of their awesome collectables.  It's a shame I had to destroy Dark Link, but it had to be done.

Enjoy the video of me smashing Dark Link.

Also be sure to Follow Me on Twitter (@KingNintendoFan) and to Like my page on Facebook.

title: Rescue Basics - Basic River Running
tags: ['Paddle (Club Interest)', 'kayaking', 'kayak', 'paddle education', 'jackson kayak', 'how to kayak', 'educational', 'instruction', 'kayak education', 'kayak instructional', 'paddle instructional', 'whitewater kayak', 'river', 'water', 'how to', 'the ferry', 'how to ferry', 'education', 'water education']
description:
Basic River Running.

Eric Jackson, will teach you how to have a great time running rivers safely in EJ's Basic River Running DVD! Lifetime kayaker and world squirt boat champion, Clay Wright, heads up the best practical safety program of all time showing you just how to keep your self out of trouble. This is the most comprehensive instructional program on equipment, logistics of river running, practical safety skills and knowledge, river reading and running skills ever assembled. We teach you the lingo of kayaking, all of the 5 major features you'll encounter, and how to easily recognize and use them on your way down the liquid conveyor belt called a river. See some of the beautiful rivers of the Southeast USA, where EJ and Clay call home. The Tellico, North Chic, Chattooga, Nantahalla, and Tallulah Rivers, and more provide our outdoor classrooms. Filmed and edited entirely by award winning videographer Chris Emerick; you will enjoy the high quality of the audio, video, and the packaging of the information to make your learning experience as enjoyable and rapid as possible.

Trata de planear su próxima película después de un éxito rotundo mientras revisa todos los momentos importantes de su vida y a todas las mujeres que han pasado por ella, como su madre (Sofía Loren), su mujer Louisa (Marion Cotillard), su musa (Nicole Kidman), una de sus amante Carla (Penélope Cruz)...

title: SaGa Frontier 2 - Showdown! Alexei
description:
I failed to record this part of the video earlier.  Sorry.  Anyway, here is the thrilling conclusion!  It really is cool!  And Alexei is hard before New Game +, not just because of the moves but because I bought a Paladin Spear in Hahn Nova (can only be done with Ginny's party) and Cody was equipped with it.

You have to have Nina in your party or you will get a game over when the Hell Wingers kill you.  I don't think you can beat the Hell Wingers, but I'm not sure.  According to Zach Keene's site, they have about 50K HP, and I'm pretty sure I've done that much damage to one with a ridiculo party, but they may regenerate.  The solution?  I have to train until I can do 50K damage with one combo.  And I will!

It's nice that SF2 is a world where people release their animas when they die instead of voiding their bowels.  RIP, Nina.  You were probably better than I gave you credit for.

title: STUDIO4FUN | La Grande Séance
description:
La Grande Séance
http://www.grandeseance.com

La Grande Séance est une journée consacrée au réseautage, à léchange dinformation et à la pratique de la photographie de studio. Cest le rendez-vous que se donnent les différents artisans de limage, i.e. photographes, maquilleurs(euses), modèles, etc. 

Tout le monde y trouve son compte : les photographes rencontrent de nouveaux modèles, partagent trucs et astuces avec leurs pairs, font lessai de différents équipements déclairage, etc. Lapprentissage du médium photographique se faisant en grande partie à travers la pratique, la Grande Séance est l'opportunité idéale pour expérimenter et poser des questions sur place.

Les images vidéos ont été prises au cours de la 12e Grande Séance (14 novembre 2010). La Grande Séance est un événement trimestriel, et la 14e Grande Séance se tiendra le 6 février 2011. Pour plus d'information : http://www.grandeseance.com

Remerciement aux conférenciers, commanditaires et bénévoles qui ont grandement contribué au succès de cet événement.

title: Giáo hoàng Francis (Phan-xi-cô) ! (Phim hoạt hình)
description:
Giáo hoàng Phanxicô (tiếng Latinh: Franciscus [franˈtʃiskus];[2]; sinh 17 tháng 12 năm 1936; tên thật: Jorge Mario Bergoglio) là giáo hoàng thứ 266 và đương kim của Giáo hội Công giáo Rôma.

Sinh tại Buenos Aires, Argentina trong một gia đình có năm anh em di dân gốc Ý. Bergoglio bắt đầu học Thần học sau khi có bằng Thạc sĩ Hóa học của Đại học Buenos Aires.[3] Ngày 11 tháng 3 1958, ông gia nhập Dòng Tên ở Argentina. Đến năm 1969, ông trở thành Linh mục và sau đó đảm nhiệm nhiều vai trò khác nhau trong Giáo hội. Từ năm 1998, ông trở thành Tổng Giám mục của Tổng giáo phận Buenos Aires. Đến năm 2001, Giáo hoàng Gioan Phaolô II phong ông làm hồng y.

Ngày 13 tháng 3 năm 2013, ông được bầu làm Giáo hoàng trong cuộc Mật nghị Hồng y sau khi Giáo hoàng Biển Đức XVI thoái vị trước đó vào ngày 28 tháng 2, thánh lễ Khai mạc sứ vụ Mục tử toàn thể Hội Thánh (lễ nhậm chức) được cử hành vào ngày 19 tháng 3, 2013, trùng vào lễ kính Thánh Giuse[4]. Vì ông sinh tại Argentina nên ông là vị Giáo hoàng đầu tiên đến từ Mỹ Latinh, đồng thời cũng là vị Giáo hoàng đầu tiên không phải từ châu Âu kể từ hơn 1200 năm qua (tính từ Giáo hoàng Grêgôriô III)[5]; và là tu sĩ Dòng Tên đầu tiên làm người kế vị Thánh Phêrô.[6] Tông hiệu của ông, Phanxicô, cũng là tông hiệu lần đầu tiên được một Giáo hoàng dùng và nó được lấy từ tên của thánh Phanxicô thành Assisi.[7]

Với tư cách là cá nhân hay là chức sắc tôn giáo, Phanxicô được đánh giá là người khiêm nhường, quan tâm đến người nghèo, và sẵn sàng đối thoại với các nhóm cộng đồng có tư tưởng, xuất thân và niềm tin khác nhau.[8][9][10] Sau khi đắc cử Giáo hoàng, ông thể hiện một tác phong giản dị hơn trong quá trình làm việc hàng ngày, chẳng hạn ông chọn nơi cư ngụ là Lưu xá Thánh Mátta (một nhà khách của Vatican) thay vì trong căn hộ dành riêng cho Giáo hoàng tại điện Tông Tòa; mặc áo lễ đơn giản hơn và từ chối mặc chiếc áo choàng sặc sỡ truyền thống dành cho Giáo hoàng sau khi đắc cử.[11] Trong chuyến viếng thăm đầu tiên tới một xứ đạo, Phanxicô nói "đây là thông điệp mạnh mẽ nhất của Thiên Chúa: tình yêu."[12] Mặc dù chỉ mới lên lãnh đạo Giáo hội Công giáo được vài tháng nhưng tạp chí danh giá Forbes đã xếp hạng Giáo hoàng Phanxicô ở vị trí thứ 4 trong số những nhân vật quyền lực nhất thế giới của năm 2013.[13], còn Tạp chí Time bình chọn ông là nhân vật của năm 2013.

title: GS - Walkthrough - Episode - 97 - Into the Venus Lighthouse
description:
-Status-
From where we enter the Babi Lighthouse to where we find our way into the Tunnel Ruins.

This is a short video on how to get past the the gate to the Tunnel entrance. Expect the next video to be a full scale walkthrough of both of the alternate entrances to the Venus Lighthouse.

Enter the Lighthouse and talk to the people lying there. Enter the Inner Lighthouse and head northeast to the door on the right. Once your done with that, head to the door on the left parellel to the door you just came out of. Then into the next door and down the slope.

Once you get down to the basement you will see Faran with a bunch of other people lookig for Sheba, the mysterious Jupiter Adept.

If you walk close enough to them you will trigger a cutscene and will show all the men there that you have the power to open the door.

After the long conversation you will be forced to go alone into the Venus Lighthouse but before that you will be forced to go through the Tunnel Ruins.

This concludes this episode. The rest will continue on episode 98.

tags: ['Dead rising 3', 'dead', 'rising', 'Sweetfx', 'sweetfx preset', 'windows 8.1', 'blur', 'directx 11', 'ssaa', 'no fxaa', 'bloom', 'enchanced', 'modded', 'graphics mod', 'custom', 'most viewed', 'playthrough', 'radeon pro', 'image improvement', 'tweaking mod', 'InjectSMAA', 'FXAAtool', 'r9 280x', 'r9 290x', 'r9 270x', 'better graphics', 'latest', 'maxed out', 'hands on', '780ti', 'performance', '390x', 'full game', 'sharpening', '4k', '60 fps', '980', '970', '960', 'preset', 'presets', 'guide', 'tutorial', 'shader', 'hdr', 'uhd', 'Lift Gamma Gain', 'Cineon DPX', 'fps', 'gameplay', 'walkthrough']
description:
Dead Rising 3 - zombi game is now visually enhanced with SweetFX preset. SweetFX works on Windows 7 / 8 / 8.1 - for both Nvidia and Amd cards!!!

Dead Rising 3 purchase link: http://unavailable/1MZQ8hg

You need to use Radeonpro with the presets. Guide is in here - 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9X1CrTYyV7o

Preset - https://www.sendspace.com/file/9xem9t
 
Join in GAMING & BENCHMARKS & SweetFX mods community-https://plus.google.com/b/109742001994795218567/communities/110598602590445579038

Follow on Twitter - https://twitter.com/multitechnopark

Like on Facebook - MultiTechnopark - GAMERS HEAVEN
https://www.facebook.com/pages/MultiTechnopark-GAMERS-HEAVEN/611017988934562?fref=ts

So in case you're new to SweetFX Shader Suite (or just SweetFX), it's a mod built on the InjectSMAA shader injector, that allows you to apply a suite of post processing shader effects to your games.
You can add SMAA anti-aliasing , sharpening and tweak the color, gamma , exposure and more.
It's meant to allow you to improve the look of your games and change the look and mood of it to your liking.
If you use SMAA antialiasing instead of MSAA or an even more expensive antialaliasing technique you can also make the game run faster (than with MSAA)

Compatibility

It works with all graphics cards as long as they support at least shader model 3. That's all cards produced after 2002 (give or take).
It does not work with 64bit game executables yet, however 64bit support should be coming in the near future - so far use the 32bit version of your game if it gives you a choice between 32 and 64bit.
It should work on Windows 2000 and newer, both 32bit and 64bit. So far tested working on WinXP , Vista , Win7 and Windows 8.
It may work on Linux using Wine - please report your findings.
It does not work well with most programs that overlay an image onto the game. It has a workaround for the Steam overlay so that will work, and you can make overlays based on Rivatuner OSD work as well with a compability setting in those overlays , but other overlays may prevent SweetFX from making changes to the image or outright crash the game - turn those off.
SweetFX is a universal image improvement and tweaking mod,
that works with almost any 32bit (and hopefully soon 64bit) DirectX 9, 10 or 11 game or application.

It's goal is provide similar tools to games in realtime, as video processing software provides for movies and videos.

Effects included:

* SMAA Anti-aliasing : Anti-aliases the image using the SMAA technique - see http://www.iryoku.com/smaa/
* FXAA Anti-aliasing : Anti-aliases the image using the FXAA technique - currently only work under DirectX9. Use the d3d9.dll found in \SweetFX\dlls\FXAA DX9 dll\ for this.
* Explosion : Scatters the pixels similarly to the Explosion filter in Irfanview
* Cartoon : Creates an outline-effect that makes the image look more cartoonish.
* Advanced CRT : Mimics the look of an old arcade CRT display.
* LumaSharpen : Sharpens the image, making details easier to see
* Bloom : Makes strong lights bleed their light into their surroundings
* HDR : Mimics an HDR tonemapped look
* Levels : Sets a new black and white point. A fast and easy way to increase contrast but it causes clipping. The Curves effect does this in a more subtle way without causing clipping.
* Technicolor : Makes the image look like it was processed using a three-strip Technicolor process - see http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Technicolor
* Cineon DPX : Makes the image look like it was converted from film to Cineon DPX. Can be used to create a "sunny" look.
* Monochrome : Removes colors from the image so it appears as if shot on black and white film.
* Lift Gamma Gain : Adjust brightness and color of shadows, midtones and highlights (and typically does it better then the Tonemap effect)
* Tonemap : Adjust gamma, exposure, saturation, bleach and defog. (may cause clipping)
* Vibrance : Intelligently saturates (or desaturates if you use negative values) the pixels depending on their original saturation.
* Curves : Contrast adjustments using S-curves - without causing clipping.
* Sepia : Sepia tones the image - see http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sepia_tone#Sepia_toning

-
Cardboard
Barbecue skewer
Drinking straw
2 CD/DVDs
Credit card or plastic store cards
Ball pen tube
Flower cane
Rubber bands
Paperclip

Main tools

Sharp knife
Junior hacksaw
Drill

title: Wario World (TAS) ~ Any% WIP
description:
Mapler90210 and I had plans to do an any% run of this game for TASVideos, but the game is yet to be emulated correctly. There are very many bugs, for example, if you stand still in a main level, it will randomly transport you to a sublevel. If you stand still there, if will give you the red crystal from that sublevel, then teleport you back up. I would continue the run anyway, but the boss for level one doesn't load and just leads to a black screen of nothingness.
Anyway, this is all we have for now. The goal is to get the required amount of red crystals for each level, and then get to the end and beat the boss. In this case, 3 red crystals is the requirement and there are 8 to choose from throughout the level.

About the run:
Dashing is obviously the fastest method of travel, hence why it is abused quite often. To my knowledge, the 2 conversations (red sprite + garlic...thing) cannot be skipped. If anyone knows how to, feel free to mention it. Mapler and I chose what we felt were the fastest sublevels (1st, 2nd, and 6th in order of appearance) for getting the 3 red crystals. I found some tricks like using the rock in the 1st sublevel to grab the blue platform, and skipping the 2 pole grabs. We are pretty satisfied with this TAS.

So far, I have been doing the TASing until Mapler gets a controller (or a TAS Input comes out), but he helped a bit with route planning, etc. Here's his channel:
http://www.youtube.com/user/mapler90210

Uploading this on my birthday. =D Happy birthday to bobmario511 as well!

title: Lagarto à La Bourguignon
tags: ['lagarto à bourguingnon', 'tastemade', 'almoco de domingo', 'almoço de domingo', 'almoço do domingo', 'carne', 'lagarto', 'lagarto cozido', 'carne com vinho tinto', 'Beef Bourguignon (Dish)']
description:
[INSCREVA-SE no canal e CURTA os vídeos!]... Adaptação ao Boeuf Bourguignon, feito de maneira mais rápida e com produtos que encontramos em todos os hipermercados.

Ingredientes:
- 01 quilo de lagarto
- 150gr de cebolinhas em conserva (na receita vão as cebolinhas, mas, não achei então comprei a que vende em conserva mesmo...rs)
- 100gr de champignon
- 200gr de bacon
- 01 cenoura
- 01 cebola
- 01 dente de alho
- cravos da índia
- Ervas: salsinha, cebolinha, louro, alecrim e hortelã
- 105ml de vinho para tempero (chef Izidro)
- 200ml de vinho tinto
- 1/2 litro de caldo de carne
- Azeite e sal a gosto.
Preparo:
Limpe a carne tirando todo excesso de gordura. Amarre a carne para ela manter o formato. Pegue uma cebola descascada e espete alguns cravos da índia, descasque uma cenoura e corte-a em pedaços (não precisa ser muito pequenos).
Faça um maço de ervas, com salsa, cebolinha, alecrim, louro e hortelã (amarre com um barbante).
Em uma panela grande sele a carne dourando-a de todos os lados em duas colheres de azeite.
Coloque a carne em uma panela de pressão e coloque a cebola, a cenoura, o ramo de ervas, o vinho para tempero e o caldo de carne (eu usei um tablete para 1/2 litro de água).
Deixe cozinhar na pressão por mais ou menos 01 hora (abaixe o fogo quando pegar pressão, não precisa ficar gastando gás e evita da carne pegar no fundo da panela).
Retire a carne da panela e corte em bifes. Coe o molho que ficou na panela (se for preciso acrescente um pouco de água antes de tirar o caldo que ficou na panela)
Pique 200gr de bacon, 100gr de champignon, 01 dente de alho.
Em uma panela grande, coloque o bacon para fritar, deixe dourar e retire (reserve-o) doure as cebolinha em conserva na gordura do bacon (reserve-as), doure o champignon nas mesma panela e reserve.
Volte os ingredientes para a panela e coloque o molho da carne. Acrescente 01 colher de amido de milho dissolvido em 150ml de água (para engrossar o molho).
(Acrescente o vinho tinto se você quiser uma quantidade maior de molho).
Coloque as carnes na panela, mexendo de vez em quando, deixe no fogo por mais 10 minutos.
Sirva com arroz ou com macarrão.
Bom Apetite!

title: Фестиваль танцев на льду 2010 "Чтобы помнили..." (Часть2)
description: Детский театр на льду «Алеко» организован в 1977 г. профсоюзным комитетом автомобильного завода имени Ленинского комсомола (АЗЛК). В 1989 г. театру присвоено звание «Образцовый художественный коллектив». В первый тренерско-педагогический состав театра входили: художественный руководитель -- заслуженная артистка РСФСР Самсонова Н.М., хореограф -- Сафонова О.В., тренеры-педагоги, мастера спорта СССР -- Карпова Е.Н., Барскова О.Л., Галкина М.О., Варьяш Н.П.. С 1998 г. художественный руководитель и режиссер-постановщик театра Кондрашова Ольга Ильинична. Свою творческую жизнь детский театр начал с композиций -- «Пусть всегда будет солнце!», «Неуловимые», «Широка страна моя родная!», «Время вперед!». Позже в репертуаре театра появились балеты «Айболит» и «Щелкунчик», концертная программа «Я иду, шагаю по Москве». Коллектив театра участвовал в художественной программе Московских Олимпийских игр, XII международного фестиваля молодежи и студентов, международных соревнований «Московские новости». В дни зимних школьных каникул театр радует маленьких москвичей красочными новогодними представлениями.

title: Nikon Small World Photomicrography Competition 2011
description:
The Nikon Small World Photomicrography Competition lets us see beyond the capabilities of our unaided eyes. Almost 2000 entries from 70 countries vied for recognition in the 37th annual contest, which celebrates photography through a microscope. Images two through 21 showcase the contest's winners in order, and are followed by a selection of other outstanding works. Scientists and photographers turned their attention on a wide range of subjects, both living and man-made, from lacewing larva to charged couple devices, sometimes magnifying them over 2000 times their original size.
(source: The Boston Globe).

Music: Visible World - Scuro - Jan Garbarek.
